Examples in this directory shows the details of process management.

1) proc1.c -- shows different ways in which a process gets terminated.

2) killproc.c -- shows how to send signals to a process.

3) sighand.c  -- shows how to handle signals.

4) sigign.c -- shows how to set that the signal need to be ignored/default
		action need to be taken.
5) readconf.c  -- shows how most of the applications re-reads conf files.


